Class DefaultRequirementContext<TTarget>

    TTarget - target type of the requirement
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ArtObject, ArtObjectContext<Requirement<TTarget>>, CombinedResultCreator, Context, Requirement<TTarget>, RequirementContext<TTarget>, ResultCreator, Scoped, TargetHolder
    public class DefaultRequirementContext<TTarget>
extends AbstractArtObjectContext<Requirement<TTarget>>
implements RequirementContext<TTarget>, CombinedResultCreator
    The requirement context is created for every unique Requirement configuration. It holds all relevant information to check the requirement and tracks the dependencies.
